Just a loveless, sad future of sadness.

130
00:10:54,029 --> 00:10:55,656
Ember, work with me.

131
00:10:55,822 --> 00:10:58,909
Your finding match
was my mother's dying wish.

132
00:10:59,451 --> 00:11:01,828
