Nice try, Mom. Got to go.

135
00:11:09,294 --> 00:11:11,129
-Save it for the wedding.
-Hey.

136
00:11:12,756 --> 00:11:13,924
Yo, yo, yo, Ember.

137
00:11:14,091 --> 00:11:15,509
Yo, Clod. Can't talk, in a hurry.

138
00:11:15,676 --> 00:11:17,469
And don't let my dad
catch you out here again.

139
00:11:17,636 --> 00:11:20,973
What? Come on,
he doesn't like my landscaping?

140
00:11:21,640 --> 00:11:22,850
