And I smell good.

144
00:11:33,277 --> 00:11:34,820
My queen.

145
00:11:37,072 --> 00:11:39,074
Sorry, buddy, elements don't mix.

146
00:11:40,868 --> 00:11:41,785
Flame.
Gotta go.

147
00:11:41,952 --> 00:11:43,954
Come on, go to the festival with me.

148
00:11:44,121 --> 00:11:45,747
