with Fire people in mind.

151
00:11:56,633 --> 00:12:00,012
Sorry, but it'd take an act of God
to get me across that bridge.

152
00:12:00,179 --> 00:12:01,263
An act of God?

153
00:12:01,430 --> 00:12:03,807
Or an act of Clod?

154
00:12:05,809 --> 00:12:06,894
Gotta run.

155
00:12:23,535 --> 00:12:24,995
As ordered.

156
00:12:29,708 --> 00:12:31,043
Gotta run.
Going for Dad's record.

157
00:12:34,129 --> 00:12:35,005
Move it!

158
00:12:53,273 --> 00:12:55,817
Winner winner, charcoal dinner...

159
00:13:20,801 --> 00:13:22,719
Head to bed, I'll close things up.

160
00:13:22,886 --> 00:13:25,764
