161
00:13:25,931 --> 00:13:28,767
Dad, I'll take care of it.
You need to rest.

162
00:13:31,228 --> 00:13:32,104
How?

163
00:13:32,271 --> 00:13:33,605
I learned from the best.

164
00:13:36,817 --> 00:13:39,486
