169
00:13:51,540 --> 00:13:54,334
If you can do that
without losing your temper...

170
00:13:54,501 --> 00:13:56,879
it will show me you are able to take over.

171
00:13:57,713 --> 00:13:58,881
You got it, <i>Àshfá.</i>

172
00:14:02,467 --> 00:14:04,845
