-Morning!

177
00:14:34,708 --> 00:14:35,876
Take a breath.

178
00:14:39,838 --> 00:14:41,048
Calm as a candle.

179
00:14:44,510 --> 00:14:46,929
Morning, welcome to The Fireplace.

180
00:14:51,850 --> 00:14:54,937
Whoa, whoa. They're all the same.
Just take one from the top.

181
00:14:55,103 --> 00:14:56,104
Thanks for shopping.

182
00:14:57,105 --> 00:14:58,732
So many stickers for sale.

183
00:14:59,983 --> 00:15:01,443
-Are these fragile?
-No, wait.

184
