have to write you a ticket.

212
00:17:07,236 --> 00:17:08,569
-A ticket?
-Yeah.

213
00:17:08,737 --> 00:17:12,074
I'm a city inspector,
and this pipe is definitely not up to code.

214
00:17:12,241 --> 00:17:15,160
I sucked a city inspector into our pipes?

215
00:17:15,327 --> 00:17:17,204
I know. Ironic, right?

216
00:17:17,371 --> 00:17:18,288
Stop messing with that.

217
00:17:18,454 --> 00:17:20,915
