-Everything's solid.

218
00:17:21,083 --> 00:17:23,752
I should know.
My dad rebuilt this place himself.

219
00:17:24,461 --> 00:17:26,588
Wait, your dad did?

220
00:17:26,755 --> 00:17:30,133
Yes, with his bare hands,
every brick and board.

221
00:17:30,300 --> 00:17:31,844
