that could get this place shut down.

227
00:17:44,523 --> 00:17:46,733
Oh, gosh. It's just too much.

228
00:17:46,900 --> 00:17:48,485
Shut us down?

229
00:17:48,652 --> 00:17:50,445
I know, it's awful.

230
00:17:50,612 --> 00:17:52,281
No, you can't shut us down, please.

231
00:17:52,447 --> 00:17:54,741
This is a big day for me.
It's our Red Dot Sale.

232
00:17:54,908 --> 00:17:58,120
Hey, take it easy.
This is as hard on me as it is on you.

233
00:17:58,287 --> 00:17:59,538
-Get back here.
-Sorry.

234
00:17:59,705 --> 00:18:02,332
