-Hey, hey!

334
00:25:38,622 --> 00:25:39,498
Sorry.

335
00:25:40,082 --> 00:25:41,208
You're so hot.

336
00:25:42,209 --> 00:25:43,085
Excuse me?

337
00:25:44,127 --> 00:25:46,255
No, I mean, like, you're smoking.

338
00:25:46,421 --> 00:25:47,464
No, I didn't mean it like that.

339
00:25:47,631 --> 00:25:49,341
-Are you done yet?
-Yes, please.

340
00:25:49,508 --> 00:25:50,926
I'm waiting to talk to your boss.

341
00:25:51,093 --> 00:25:54,054
So, make like a stream
and flow somewhere else.

342
00:25:54,221 --> 00:25:55,889
Actually, Gale won't be in today.

343
00:25:56,056 --> 00:25:57,808
She's a huge airball fan...

344
00:25:57,975 --> 00:26:00,310
and the Windbreakers
are finally in the playoffs.

345
00:26:00,477 --> 00:26:01,812
Toot toot.

346
00:26:02,646 --> 00:26:04,606
Okay. Well, I just came by...

347
00:26:04,773 --> 00:26:07,192
because I left my passes
for the game here last night.

348
00:26:07,651 --> 00:26:09,862
