-Jimmy, what's up?

358
00:27:03,790 --> 00:27:05,834
-Sorry. Pardon.
-Wendy.

359
00:27:06,001 --> 00:27:07,961
Sorry. Fire girl coming through.

360
00:27:08,128 --> 00:27:10,797
Break some wind!

361
00:27:10,964 --> 00:27:12,299
Hi, Gale, how you doing?

362
00:27:12,466 --> 00:27:14,259
Look at the score, what do you think?

363
00:27:14,426 --> 00:27:16,762
Blow the ball, not the game!

364
00:27:18,055 --> 00:27:20,599
Yeah, so, Gale.

365
00:27:21,266 --> 00:27:24,770
My name is Ember Lumen.
My family runs a Fire shop.

366
00:27:24,937 --> 00:27:26,730
