with 30 citations.

369
00:27:32,027 --> 00:27:33,445
Thirty?

370
00:27:33,612 --> 00:27:37,658
Anyway, friend, I was hoping
we could work something out.

371
00:27:37,824 --> 00:27:41,036
Come on, ref!
Are your eyes in the back of your head?

372
00:27:43,830 --> 00:27:45,874
-Oh, no.
-Yeah, bummer.

373
00:27:46,041 --> 00:27:48,961
Yeah. Okay, so, the 30 citations.

374
00:27:49,127 --> 00:27:52,840
Do you mind? There's a game going on.
Fireball.

375
00:27:53,423 --> 00:27:54,383
Fireball?

376
00:27:55,384 --> 00:27:56,885
Actually, I do mind.

377
00:27:57,052 --> 00:28:00,013
This is my life we're talking about.
Not just some game.

378
00:28:00,180 --> 00:28:02,808
Some game?
This is the playoffs.

379
00:28:02,975 --> 00:28:05,644
So, forgive me
if I don't want to hear a sob story...

380
00:28:05,811 --> 00:28:08,438
about the problems of some little shop.

381
00:28:08,605 --> 00:28:11,483
Well, that little shop matters way more...

382
00:28:11,650 --> 00:28:14,736
than a bunch of overpaid cloud puffs
blowing some ball around.

383
00:28:14,903 --> 00:28:16,405
I dare you...

384
00:28:16,572 --> 00:28:19,908
