385
00:28:20,617 --> 00:28:22,870
Cloud puffs.

386
00:28:24,830 --> 00:28:26,081
Oh, no!

387
00:28:26,248 --> 00:28:27,082
Lutz!

388
00:28:38,010 --> 00:28:41,680
Lutz, man. He's been in such a funk
'cause his mom has been sick.

389
00:28:45,267 --> 00:28:49,104
That is so not cool, he's doing his best.

390
00:28:49,271 --> 00:28:52,482
We love you, Lutz!

391
00:28:52,649 --> 00:28:54,818
Lutz!

392
00:28:55,444 --> 00:28:58,322
We love you, Lutz!

393
00:28:58,488 --> 00:29:01,200
We love you, Lutz!
Come on!

394
00:29:01,366 --> 00:29:04,077
We love you, Lutz! Everybody!

395
00:29:04,244 --> 00:29:07,706
We love you, Lutz!
We love you, Lutz!

396
00:29:07,831 --> 00:29:10,792
We love you, Lutz!
We love you, Lutz!

